{"tid":637884,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"邊條仆街老婆死左隻poodle又即刻買返隻約瑟俾佢？","createTime":"2018-04-22T08:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T04:52:36.000Z","uid":1964,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"59d8046da5a50bc299a14478d75d5ecf610a5f01","tid":637884,"uid":1964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:38:45.000Z","msg":"如果你見到呢個post<br />\n我希望你條冚家產好好反省下<br />\n<br />\n你老婆死撚左隻poodle<br />\n你見佢咁唔開心，就即刻成皮幾嘢買返隻約瑟俾佢<br />\n<br />\n而家你老婆話傷心未過，唔想接受新寵物<br />\n你就掉佢去啲狗場搵人接收<br />\n<br />\n而家輾轉隻嘢喺我屋企(唔係我帶返嚟)<br />\n為我屋企帶嚟好大既麻煩<br />\n<br />\n唔知你會唔會為你既on9而後悔<br />\n但我話你知，你一定會俾天收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1ca0254e6685ada95362a41c244381294e4e9b","tid":637884,"uid":1964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:41:00.000Z","msg":"就係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/164045_f4cd41a2af170348c8e0f5a91241fa45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F164045_f4cd41a2af170348c8e0f5a91241fa45.png&h=2006039c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"245b0f7efc45941b6c4288aee20bcce8c54af57c","tid":637884,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:52:50.000Z","msg":"如果死咗我諗我都應該唔想再養下一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個老公真係幾on9<br />\n<br />\n利申有兩隻都係親人無辦法再養去咗我度"},{"pid":"38d89c1ed0a74d8d56ccbcac908ca35ff0f8f0d3","tid":637884,"uid":1964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"245b0f7efc45941b6c4288aee20bcce8c54af57c","tid":637884,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:52:50.000Z","msg":"如果死咗我諗我都應該唔想再養下一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個老公真係幾on9<br />\n<br />\n利申有兩隻都係親人無辦法再養去咗我度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:49:00.000Z","msg":"On9兼不負責任<br />\n